@MarylineKassp Hello Maryline, 
I'm sorry to hear you haven't received a response yet. Please send us the reference number of your claim (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) via PM and we'll have a look.
Best regards, Gayle

@JoseleBernabe Hello Josele,
I'm sorry to hear you haven't received a response yet. Please send us the reference number of your claim (XXXX-OS-XXXXX) via PM and we'll have a closer look.
Best regards, Gayle

@x61sh Hello there, 
thanks for reaching out. How can we help you?
Best regards, Gayle

@RCLTILBURG Hi Boelie, 
We are sorry to hear that the boarding couldn't start on time. However, we can see that the flight still arrived earlier than scheduled in Vienna. If you need further assistance, please let us know. 
Best regards, Shawn

@EmilLayacan @AirCanada (1/3) Hello Emil,
 I'm sorry to hear about your delayed luggage. We are unable to assist with baggage cases, we kindly ask you to stay in touch with the number on your Lost Report for any updates. You may alternatively check the current status online here
https://t.co/hrzpeIKQj2

@MarvSays Hello Marv, 
I'm sorry to hear you missed your flight. Please don't get us wrong, we are in no way blaming you, however, please be advised that boarding usually has to be completed 10 minutes before departure time. 
Best regards, Gayle

@bentleybrowning Dear Bentley,
I already sent a note of urgency to the respective department. I hope you'll receive an answer soon. 
Best regards, Alessandra

@joetyle59406835 @FlorenceAirport Hi again JT,
I am sorry to hear that. The Social Media Team does not have access to the baggage system. You can check the status of your baggage online via this link https://t.co/hrzpeJ2Zxa 
Best regards, Alessandra

@CuteDumbBat Hi there, 
Thank you for getting in touch. As far as we know, there is currently no report of any breakdowns given. Please let us know if there is anything else we can help you with. 
Best regards, Shawn

@vagelis_h Hi there, 
Thank you for providing us with your reference number. We have received your submission correctly and it is lined up for the process. Please be informed that we have forwarded your submission with urgency to our respective colleagues.  
Best regards, Shawn

@heri5ca Hello,
I'm sorry that you are already waiting for so long. Please send me your file reference number XXXX-OS-XXXXXX so we can have a closer look at your complaint.
 Kind regards, Alessandra
